            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A9%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%B7%E5%A7%86%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%8B%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A9%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%B7%E5%A7%86%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%8B%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#大人小孩适用的海姆立克法不一样#</span></a>】近日，江苏一14岁女孩一招救下异物卡喉弟弟，让“海姆立克急救法”再度被热议。如果被噎或被卡住，使用这一方法可帮助气道异物排出。需注意的是，针对3岁以下小孩和成人，海姆立克急救法的动作并不相同。此外，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8%E6%B5%B7%E5%A7%86%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%8B%E6%B3%95%E8%87%AA%E6%95%91%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8%E6%B5%B7%E5%A7%86%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%8B%E6%B3%95%E8%87%AA%E6%95%91%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#一个人也可用海姆立克法自救#</span></a>！学起来👇🏻关键时刻能救命！ <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4909031249346563" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hemjkvx0xmj61er0sktqj02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/YYzzwfFblx085YMMLhKU01041200iBIC0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685942300&amp;ssig=OWDQMIWRMS&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/71xz6SSHlx085YMLWiuk010412009jvV0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685942300&amp;ssig=%2FwyYPf9nsa&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/16XSOrYolx085YMLkpdm010412005Tht0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685942300&amp;ssig=wS0n%2B4U0MN&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4909031249346563&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
